RRandomRHighestProfit
Ruins a random number of alleles (which is guaranteed to be smaller than MAXIMUM_RR_PERCENTAGE * population_size), and recreates by including n highest profit items in the ruined set in knapsack, while n is exactly the number of items that are excluded by the ruin step
RRandomRHighestVPW
Ruins a random number of alleles (which is guaranteed to be smaller than MAXIMUM_RR_PERCENTAGE * population_size), and recreates by including n highest 'profit per weight' items in the ruined set in knapsack, while n is exactly the number of items that are excluded by the ruin step
RRandomRLowestWeight
Ruins a random number of alleles (which is guaranteed to be smaller than MAXIMUM_RR_PERCENTAGE * population_size), and recreates by including n lowest weight items in the ruined set in knapsack, while n is exactly the number of items that are excluded by the ruin step
RRandomRRandom
Ruins a random number of alleles (which is guaranteed to be smaller than MAXIMUM_RR_PERCENTAGE * population_size) and recreate them of random 0 or 1
